{"tid":1648560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地有希望,再努力D就會贏","createTime":"2019-10-12T09:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T15:01:05.000Z","uid":238920,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1dffb300d4a1715f73dac4ed777fdf81937aa1","tid":1648560,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:17:19.000Z","msg":"我地已經贏緊<br />\n我地已經望到個終點<br />\n港共所有手段都冇計,中國內憂外患,外國大反華<br />\n雖然離終點仲有距離,只要一步一步繼續前行,一定會達到目標<br />\n但係<br />\n贏緊唔代表我地乜都唔洗做<br />\n總之兄弟爬山,各有各做<br />\n我地冇時間去自怨自艾去內鬥內消<br />\n我地要去返6.9咁,明知不可為而為之<br />\n謹慎思考,大膽行事<br />\n團結,合作,不分化,不割蓆<br />\n終有一日,一定會為香港人拎返應有既野,為我地死左既手兄討回公道<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於太多負面撚放負撚,我希望大家正面d,同時咪再輸輸輸"},{"pid":"1d84f00254d3c75f208e8b7bb9a862d0dabedb9e","tid":1648560,"uid":710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65b6a91176700cd0114fab3e08df51cf89c6f73","tid":1648560,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n相信乜野有用就繼續做<br />\n堅持落去"},{"pid":"23132696897fe9e09f3c33814f1417459a36acd5","tid":1648560,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:12:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb6a92b41fe6dbe94b91caef919711a2d8a0302d","tid":1648560,"uid":325026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"呢排真係唔記得咗be water...要記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}